General.Name: Carbon Revolution Ltd
General.Description: Carbon Revolution Limited designs, manufactures, sells, and markets lightweight carbon fibre wheels to original equipment manufacturers worldwide. The company's products are used in automotive, electric vehicle, motorsports, heavy vehicle, and aerospace industries. It also provides associated engineering services; sells tools related to wheels; and undertakes research and development projects related to carbon fibre wheel technology. The company was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Waurn Ponds, Australia.
